methods.gatherDictionaryValuesIndex:
Optional method that should only be used on regions returned by ColumnRegionObject.getDictionaryValuesRegion().
 Gathers

:param keysToVisit: (io.deephaven.engine.rowset.RowSet.SearchIterator) - A search iterator over the enclosing table address space (which must have the same
                          regions at the same masks), positioned at a rowSet key in this region. Used to
                          identify regions to visit. Should be advanced to after this region as a side-effect.
:param knownKeys: (io.deephaven.engine.rowset.RowSequence.Iterator) - An iterator over the previously-known rowSet keys, positioned at the first known key in
                          this region, or after the region's maximum key if no keys are known. Should be advanced
                          to after this region as a side effect.
:param sequentialBuilder: (io.deephaven.engine.rowset.RowSetBuilderSequential) - Output builder; implementations should append ranges for rowSet keys not found in
                          knownKeys
:return: (boolean) Whether keysToVisit has been exhausted
methods.getDictionaryKeysRegion: :return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.impl.sources.regioned.ColumnRegionLong<io.deephaven.engine.chunk.Attributes.DictionaryKeys>) A dictionary keys region as specified by ColumnRegionObject.supportsDictionaryFormat(RowSet.SearchIterator)
